# ── Host normalization: force www → bare (canonical host) ──
# Canonical tags and sitemap both point at https://dependability.us/ (bare).
# The actual www → bare 301 is enforced by a Cloudflare Page Rule on the
# dependability.us zone (target: www.dependability.us/*, action:
# forwarding_url 301 to https://dependability.us/$1). CF Pages `_redirects`
# only matches paths, not hosts, so a host-level redirect cannot be expressed
# here. The line below is a defense-in-depth no-op kept for documentation; it
# is silently ignored by Pages and the Page Rule is the source of truth.
https://www.dependability.us/* https://dependability.us/:splat 301!

